# Local-only Android TWA build projects (Gradle caches, signing keystores,
# compiled APKs/AABs) — not part of the deployed web app, stays local.
# android-twa/ wraps FT (GitHub Pages), android-twa-wellness/ wraps
# wellness.winfinityfitness.com, android-twa-messenger/ wraps
# messenger.winfinityfitness.com — separate Play Store apps/keystores, same
# reasoning for staying out of the repo.
android-twa/
android-twa-wellness/
android-twa-messenger/

# Local-only Capacitor native Android shell (loads the live site remotely,
# adds real background GPS tracking via a native plugin the bare TWA above
# can't do). node_modules and the generated Gradle project are regenerable
# via `npm install` + `npx cap add android` — not part of the deployed web
# app, stays local. package.json/capacitor.config.json are tracked.
capacitor-app/node_modules/
capacitor-app/android/
